YAML in Torvalds's Tree (mainline)
https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux.git/tree/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/media/i2c/sony,imx219.yaml
Driver in C in Torvalds's Tree (mainline)
https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux.git/tree/drivers/media/i2c/imx219.c

DTS (Device Tree Strucure) for the official NXP i.MX 8 M Plus evaluation board.
https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux.git/tree/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/imx8mp-evk.dts
Note that several DTSI and DTSO files with names beginning imx8mp-evk are available for different configurations in the freescale directory - named before the Freescale NXP merger:
https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux.git/tree/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/

